               Rev. 16 10, 11. I believe is this learning which we have here in queſtion, for as we have before manifeſted, the Sun light of the Goſpel of Jeſus Chriſt allows not, for the glory of Chriſts Doctrine is, that it is of the Spirits teaching;
               2 Cor. 3 12. for when we behold the glory of the Lord in the moſt perfect meaſure, ſo as we are changed thereinto from glory to glory; yet all is from the Spirit of the Lord, ſeeing that he is the promiſed Comforter, that is to teach us all good things belonging to our perfection.
